@102568 = ~Mace of Repose +4~/*Fortuna degli eroi*/
@102569 = ~This mace is made by the finest blacksmiths in Neverwinter. The gods themselves must have helped the blacksmith in his work. He was able to forge a mace of repose from an unremarkable mace, but he used the special holy water we found. This mace is a terrible dream for all evil forces, it can destroy the undead with a single blow and causes a lot of additional damage to all demonic creatures. To be fair, it cannot destroy higher level undead (above level 20).

