@102962 = ~Bacchetta Bruciante di Karlat~
@102963 = ~This wand is an extremely simple to use wand that casts the spell Burning Hands. The wand need only be waved and no arcane knowledge is required to use it. It was likely the very first wand given to a young apprentice mage.

