@103009 = ~This large blade is a sword that has passed through the hands of many generations of great knights. When the blade is passed on, the old owner drips blood from his wound, which he inflicted on himself according to ritual, onto the blade. The blood has given this blade magical properties that are passed on to the owner of the blade.

