@103047 = ~This great sword was given to you by the spirit of Maegel, who in the distant past defeated the terrible Black Lich with this sword, but fell in battle with his minions. No lich can resist the blows of this sword, and it is so comfortable in the hand that even those who are not skilled in the use of bastard swords can use it.

