@103762 = ~Alatis' Guard~/*Guardia alla Porta*/
@103763 = ~Alatis Harbleton was one of the many halflings who had chosen a profession that was not to be mentioned in pleasant conversation. He had made a good career in Luskan, until a series of unpleasant events forced him to consider relocating to a new place.

Settling within the walls of the capital city of Waterdeep, he continued his activities. His willingness to act alone in making ill-gotten gains infuriated local guilds such as the infamous Night Masks, so he had to enlist a wizard to enchant his hood to protect himself from frequent attempts on his life.

Arrogant and confident in his invulnerability, he nevertheless got caught in a daring robbery and was caught by the guards. Unfortunately, his hood did not save him from the hangman's noose.

